description: My oh my! D'Pana Cachapas is vrooming through Miami and bringing the best Venezuelan food to the beaches. They’re serving up traditional favorites such as Arepas (delicious fluffy corn cakes that are stuffed with various fillings; cheeses, meats, vegetables, etc…) Patacones (fried plantain slices; the perfect sweet and savory bite) and wonderful Empanadas. Don’t forget to refresh yourself with the hard-to-find traditional sodas of Venezuela, like Malta. For a vibrantly scrumptious Venezuelan meal that you’re sure to love, come check out D'Pana Cachapas.
name: D'Pana Cachapas
